        a                        fabio:Figure ;
        dc:description           "Figure 2. (A) Monobrachium parasitum: fertile colony (with gonophore) adhering to a pelecypod shell; (B) the pelecypod Mendicula ferruginosa; (C) one-tentacled polyp: at the left side the entire polyp, at the right side the tentacle; (D) detail of the tentacle, with microbasic eurytele nematocysts. (Colour online)" ;
        fabio:hasRepresentation  "https://zenodo.org/record/4631878/files/figure.png" .
